query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS website (
            id    INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            url  TEXT NOT NULL ,
            task_id  INTEGER NOT NULL,
            favicon  TEXT,
            title TEXT,
            status_code INTEGER,
            headers TEXT,
            finger TEXT,
            screenshot TEXT,
            tags TEXT,
            ssl_info TEXT,
            create_at INTEGER,                                      
            update_at INTEGER,
            UNIQUE (url)
        );
